{"tid":2436964,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【求下你地】成日都４７人４７人４７人４７人４７人，４７人個光環係咪大啲？？？？","createTime":"2021-03-07T14:01:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-07T16:30:05.000Z","uid":88743,"like":12,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"fbb674cd631a3108f86e3ee86b8a9cbd2963ed2b","tid":2436964,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T14:01:37.000Z","msg":"泛民前幾日吹雞即刻有千幾人和應<br />\n發揮佢地動員力俾中共睇<br />\n完美展示到係國安法同限眾令下<br />\n佢地仍然可以動員香港黃營既人用腳支持<br />\n<span class=\"small\"><strong>（支持泛民既話就可以出黎<br />\n遊行示威反極權既話就有國安法限聚令好危險）</strong></span><br />\n呢種動員能力展示佢地對泛民既愛（泛民動員）<br />\n就係佢地係中共眼中既價值<br />\n<br />\n佢地SHOW　OFF　香港人對佢地既支持<br />\n想話俾中共知佢地係香港維穩仲有價值<br />\n（當然唔係講緊４７人入面每一個人）<br />\n如果中共搵佢地做人質外交同美國枱底談判<br />\n如果覺得４７人仍然仲係有用<br />\n促成談判放生或輕判部份人既機會都係會大增<br />\n<br />\n卿姐：香港人應繼續和平理性非暴力爭取民主<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區 <br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2434187\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2434187</a><br />\n其他泛民已經開始鋪緊路<br />\nExpectation management,　一定係搵個最令人反感既人吹撚到最撚極端先<br />\n之後再搵啲企開中間既，民望高少少既人UP兩句人話拉返去中間講<br />\n「其實香港真係無空間再街頭抗爭」「唔想香港人再無辜受傷被捕」之類<br />\n黃營既劉慧卿＝藍營既啖慧珠<br />\n功能一樣<br />\n<br />\n但無可否認呢個都係佢地自保既方法<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"violet\">但係九十二籤呢？<br />\n今日成個熱門都唔撚見佢地既？？？<br />\n<br />\n第197日｜聽日九十二籤上庭你知唔知呀?<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區 <br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2436593\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2436593</a> <br />\n<br />\n４７人個光環係咪大啲？？？？？！？！？！？！？！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"dd305a6f7a18d9ee24e9f2eb1f99d54a05357ca3","tid":2436964,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T14:07:03.000Z","msg":"無人知邊個九十二簽？"},{"pid":"36f7677db6726bbde5338a42480cb7184e8a4003","tid":2436964,"uid":389613,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T14:08:50.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">樓主係著名白兵打手 母看沸鹽<br />\n專門借意挑釁，離間陣營團結<br />\n等條契弟單機就得，見字勿回，感謝</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<ins>證據如下：<br />\n</ins><br />\n<ins>手足比人 DQ 就落井下石，走去吹噓白兵：</ins><br />\n<br />\n３５＋計劃大成功，係時候為白兵平反<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2132084\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2132084</a><br />\n<br />\n<ins>47 人比人拉，就唔比人去聲援：</ins><br />\n<br />\n【緊急】民陣又緊急呼籲香港人對全港最大忠誠反對派既忠誠度！！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2426768\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2426768</a><br />\n<br />\n<ins>泛民比人拉，繼續落井下石：</ins><br />\n<br />\n【非分化】今日係連登吹奏過黃碧雲既，你地無資格講民主！！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2427125\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2427125</a><br />\n<br />\n<ins>收左 Order 邊個 KOL 訂閱量多就攻擊：</ins><br />\n<br />\n點睇兩大時事youtuber吳志森黃世澤，一個24萬訂閱另一個8萬，但平均收視倒撚返轉一個3萬幾另一個5萬UP？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2234734\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2234734</a><br />\n<br />\n<ins>同時又收錢幫支持國安法既 KOL 洗底：</ins><br />\n<br />\n【國際線=虛偽】神駒直線抽擊國際線對就侵就兇狠，拜登對華「策略性忍耐」就視而不見！！！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2388437\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2388437</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">拉</span></span><br />\n<br />\nSOURCE:<br />\n#228 回覆 - 如果見到有通街都知係五毛/PR嘅狗隻<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/rcLiBsX\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/rcLiBsX</a>"},{"pid":"29e54ae1e4853042c52b56388508d467ffc33378","tid":2436964,"uid":54721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T14:09:57.000Z","msg":"其他手足呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64fd46c5b8cb4e4f6d2aa7647f355f82d0c2c8bf","tid":2436964,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T14:12:05.000Z","msg":"講事實都係惡意挑釁！？！？！？<br />\n叫你地班人關注下九十二籤又係惡挑釁！？！？！？<br />\n你係咪捉鬼天師？？？？？？？？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NGWKJTo.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNGWKJTo.gif&h=64d7183e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a6ee1cc3416f33c3c1cf6d54f8df37df725a15b9","tid":2436964,"uid":88743,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29e54ae1e4853042c52b56388508d467ffc33378","tid":2436964,"uid":54721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T14:09:57.000Z","msg":"其他手足呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T14:14:05.000Z","msg":"因為係九十二籤係聽日<br />\n比較緊急<br />\n所以講左先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n平時見呢啲送車PO都過百正評<br />\n今次果個得幾十<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為係九十二籤<br />\n所以大家小心限聚令<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb2a6a6bc2e9fdad0cf94237af9d04f8e00757be","tid":2436964,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T14:16:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e23604cff55b282e9f5189aa83b87ed37848b5e","tid":2436964,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T14:20:41.000Z","msg":"咁撚多負皮<br />\n原來４７人光環真係大啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dbdfb6e5f481e1856e225262fdc5c7b3d16e9f7","tid":2436964,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T14:24:28.000Z","msg":"第197日｜聽日九十二籤上庭你知唔知呀?<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區 <br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2436593\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2436593</a><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>今日繼續無十二人消息, 既然九十二籤上庭咁大件事無乜人知, 咁我話你知喇<br />\n❙ 當年今日<br />\n#20200307爆炸<br />\n今日2021年3月7日，上年油塘,其他區有鬼私出沒，多人被恐怖綁上車，有人嗌救命，其中6人涉爆炸案，其中4人還押至今一年。<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12114\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F12114&d=nX%2BkuNaC9t4xEeYfS0E7bDvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=c3b89c38\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12114</a><br />\n佢哋事隔一年聽日再上庭（首次上庭係星期三沙田）<br />\n有人被虐至失去視力，有人雙腿骨折坐輪椅（九龍城下午突發提堂）上庭仍堅持站立，有人被毆被恐嚇之類，各種虐待行為都集齊晒。<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_mailbox/153\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_mailbox%2F153&d=nX%2BkuNaC9t4xEeYfS0E7bDvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=38f7a57f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_mailbox/153</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">突然諗起，佢哋為咗封關，為救醫護為救港人為咗信念為香港，結果香港人係完全無視，望下聽日送車人數有幾多就知，再對比一下西九啲明星。</span></span></strong><br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://t.me/neverforgivepopodklm/710\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fneverforgivepopodklm%2F710&d=nX%2BkuNaC9t4xEeYfS0E7bDvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=c0fed705\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/neverforgivepopodklm/710</a><br />\n<br />\n❙ 上次上庭資訊: <br />\n#東區裁判法院第一庭  <br />\n#錢禮主任裁判官<br />\n#20200307爆炸 #提堂<br />\n<br />\nD1 何 (36) 🛑已還押逾9個月<br />\nD2 李 (25) 🛑已還押逾9個月<br />\nD3 吳 (27) 🛑已還押逾9個月<br />\nD4 張 (29) 🛑已還押逾9個月<br />\nD5 楊 (28) ✅24/4保釋獲批<br />\nD6 張 (24) ✅24/6保釋獲批<br />\n<br />\n控罪：<br />\n(1) 串謀導致相當可能會危害生命或財產的爆炸 (違反刑事罪行條例 第53條及第159A條) [D1-D6]<br />\n(2) 管有物品意圖摧毀或損壞財產 (違反刑事罪行條例 第62(a)條) [D3, D6]<br />\n(3) 管有物品意圖摧毀或損壞財產 (違反刑事罪行條例 第62(a)條) [D2]<br />\n<br />\n🛑D1-D4沒保釋申請，繼續還押🛑<br />\n✅D6更改擔保人獲批✅<br />\n✅D5,6減少報到次數獲批✅<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">案件押後至 2021年3月8日1430 東區裁判法院第一庭再訊</span></strong></span><br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12114\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F12114&d=nX%2BkuNaC9t4xEeYfS0E7bDvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=c3b89c38\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12114</a> <br />\n<br />\n❙ 【還押手足給大家的公開信】- SNAKE<br />\n<br />\n致各位同路人：<br />\n<br />\n大家好，我是其中一位捲入邊境爆炸案的手足，就是被探員在警署黑布蒙頭打了數分鐘，現在左眼失去部份視力那位。<br />\n<br />\n今天是4月8日，我永遠忘不了一個月前那天，在和女友相約共渡良宵的晚上，會和家人及心愛的人相隔分開一段長時間，會被五名探員黑布蒙頭暴打數分鐘，會被腳踢心口兩次，會被腳踏下體兩次，會被大力把頭撞到枱面一次，左面額頭會被大力拳打兩次，結果導致左眼失去三成視野角度，見到光源會頭痛，偶然會失焦，這些一般人不會想像到的暴力對待，是可以突然降臨到你身上，當你住在一個充滿警暴的城市。<br />\n<br />\n大家可能會問我感受如何，當然是很傷心，很憤怒，但其實比起被射爆眼睛的女FA和印尼女記者，我受的痛和傷算得上什麼？還有被打到掉牙的小兄弟，中槍的健仔和熊仔餅， 721被打到頭破血流的路人，每一個都比我承受更大的痛苦！我最大的希望是，請你們不要忘記我們每一個流的血，受的傷好嗎？五大訴求，我們爭取到了多少？請記着我們受的傷，我們失去的自由，親情和愛情，只要你們不放棄，我們在鐵籠中也會堅持下去！<br />\n<br />\n你若不離（開）<br />\n我定不（放）棄！<br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命！<br />\n<br />\nSNAKE<br />\n8/4/2020<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N5tMVvc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN5tMVvc.jpg&h=968d4dfe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_mailbox/153\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_mailbox%2F153&d=nX%2BkuNaC9t4xEeYfS0E7bDvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=38f7a57f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_mailbox/153</a><br />\n<br />\n❙ 關注被捕人士: <a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk&d=nX%2BkuNaC9t4xEeYfS0E7bDvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=efac54d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk</a><br />\n-【#聲援預告 2021.03.09-2021.03.12】-  <a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk/20401\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk%2F20401&d=nX%2BkuNaC9t4xEeYfS0E7bDvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=950ea57a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk/20401</a><br />\n-【2021.03.08 其他法庭聲援留意今晚法庭post】<br />\n❙ 最後聯署要人: <br />\n中大聯署: <a href=\"https://linktr.ee/Sfuhk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flinktr.ee%2FSfuhk&d=nX%2BkuNaC9t4xEeYfS0E7bDvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=78f51580\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://linktr.ee/Sfuhk</a><br />\nSim Card 實名制: <a href=\"http://fb.com/3953636308009406\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2F3953636308009406&d=nX%2BkuNaC9t4xEeYfS0E7bDvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=b09236c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">fb.com/3953636308009406</a><br />\n❙ Twitter 要人香港影子議會 Hong Kong Shadow Parliament: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/HKShadowParl?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHKShadowParl%3Fs%3D20&d=nX%2BkuNaC9t4xEeYfS0E7bDvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=509873f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/HKShadowParl?s=20</a><br />\n❙ 懲罰師出動- Pazu 薯伯伯<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/2007814566118012/posts/3147564215476369/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F2007814566118012%2Fposts%2F3147564215476369%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=nX%2BkuNaC9t4xEeYfS0E7bDvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=655ca444\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/2007814566118012/posts/3147564215476369/?d=n</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"0e2058b80544295e98e158d46253d58e8f28594d","tid":2436964,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T14:26:49.000Z","msg":"47個重要人物而係裡面連野都冇得扑<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇咸書打飛機都冇興趣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50f6f006cd69f06de609d5edde930adec567cb5d","tid":2436964,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T14:31:53.000Z","msg":"為求封關　羅湖站發現懷疑爆炸品　TG 頻道「九十二籤」認責　警：向恐怖主義行近一大步<br />